{"id":2003,"date":"2020-11-28T15:26:00","date_gmt":"2020-11-28T14:26:00","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/studio-size.com\/?post_type=work&#038;p=2003"},"modified":"2024-06-13T11:07:57","modified_gmt":"2024-06-13T09:07:57","slug":"flawless-typography","status":"publish","type":"work","link":"https:\/\/studio-size.com\/work\/flawless-typography\/","title":{"rendered":"Flawless Typography"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<section class=\"intro-block\" data-fade-reveal>\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <div class=\"columns\">\n            <div class=\"column one\">\n                <div class=\"client-wrap\">\n                                            <p class=\"b1 small\">Client<\/p>\n                                                                <p class=\"b0 client fw-500\">Bornfight<\/p>\n                                    <\/div>\n                <div class=\"services-wrap\">\n                                            <p class=\"b1 small\">Services<\/p>\n                                                                <p class=\"b0 services fw-500\">Motion<\/p>\n                                    <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n            <div class=\"column two\">\n                                    <p class=\"b0  fw-500\">\n                        Mario \u0160estak&#8217;s is an experienced designer who created an online class called &#8220;Flawless Typography&#8221;. It is a part of the Awwwards academy online courses for designers and developers. To promote Mario&#8217;s class, we created a video trailer. The idea was to place typography at the center of the video, so we dug through Mario&#8217;s portfolio to explore the various typography he used in his designs. Then we employed his typographic treatments to highlight the key messages of the video&#8217;s narration. That way, the viewer can focus equally on both the audio and visual aspects. With the footage, Mario&#8217;s voiceover, and typographic subtitling, we simultaneously introduce viewers to their teacher and the quality of his work. The video is a collaboration with Mario \u0160estak and Bornfight agency.                    <\/p>\n                            <\/div>\n        <\/div>\n    <\/div>\n<\/section>\n\n\n\n<section class=\"full-width-inline-video-block\" data-fade-reveal>\n    <div class=\"container\">\n                    <video src=\"https:\/\/player.vimeo.com\/progressive_redirect\/playback\/678229156\/rendition\/720p\/file.mp4?loc=external&#038;log_user=0&#038;signature=916e0b01124cd60a9c3ffa1c1e9cf2c93e5e70a82d14aca6abc649be0bdaa4be\" muted loop playsinline class=\"on-scroll\"><\/video>\n            <\/div>\n<\/section>\n\n\n\n<section class=\"image-text-block\" data-fade-reveal>\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <div class=\"wrapper right\">\n                            <img decoding=\"async\" width=\"873\" height=\"491\" src=\"https:\/\/studio-size.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/White-Background-873x491.jpg\" class=\"attachment-case-img-text size-case-img-text\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/studio-size.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/White-Background-873x491.jpg 873w, https:\/\/studio-size.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/White-Background-300x169.jpg 300w, https:\/\/studio-size.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/White-Background-1024x576.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/studio-size.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/White-Background-768x432.jpg 768w, https:\/\/studio-size.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/White-Background-1281x720.jpg 1281w, https:\/\/studio-size.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/White-Background-117x66.jpg 117w, https:\/\/studio-size.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/White-Background.jpg 1400w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 873px) 100vw, 873px\" \/>                                    <div class=\"text\">\n                <h4 class=\"a2\">We balanced filmed footage and motion graphics for optimal contrast.<\/h4>\n            <\/div>\n                    <\/div>\n    <\/div>\n<\/section>\n\n\n\n<section class=\"two-images